&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purpose of Position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Lead Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to help define and build a distinctive accessories language for the brand across customisable products, charms, add-ons, small leather goods, and related lifestyle accessories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is for a designer with the ability to create products that feel &lt;strong&gt;recognizable, refined, and enduring&lt;/strong&gt;—not simply attractive or trend-responsive. The successful candidate will combine strong creative authorship with disciplined execution, shaping products that express clear brand codes, elevated materiality, and a coherent collectible logic across core, seasonal, and limited programs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This person will own the design process &lt;strong&gt;from&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;concept through launch&lt;/strong&gt;, while contributing to a broader product language that can scale over time. They must be capable of designing both individual hero pieces and modular systems that build long-term brand equity through consistency, desirability, and thoughtful evolution.&lt;/p&gt;
