&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Design &amp;amp; Creative Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead design of accessories and customisable products from concept development through sampling, refinement, and launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create products with a clear sense of authorship, distinction, and brand recognizability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop hero pieces as well as supporting product families that reinforce a larger collection narrative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate brand codes, storytelling direction, and category ambition into products with clarity, restraint, and depth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
