&lt;li&gt;Define how products connect, evolve, and expand across seasons and drops without losing coherence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design with long-term system thinking, ensuring products contribute to a cumulative and ownable brand world.&lt;/li&gt;
